Name: UCSB
Description: A great university located along the California coast.

Name: Papalote
Description: Unique burritos with some of the smoothest salsa anywhere.

Name: La Taqueria
Description: Best traditional mission burritos on the planet.

Name: In-N-Out Burger
Description: Best place to visit for takeout before traveling across the Golden Gate bridge, then eating lunch at the viewpoint area

Name: Freebirds
Description: Somehow, I've eaten here more than almost any other restaurant in my life, yet don't know if I'd actually recommend its burritos to others

Name: Freebirds
Description: Apparently the Freebirds in Isla Vista is an offshoot of another, competing Freebirds burrito chain. I can vouch that they test nothing like each other. The whole situation seems a bit complicated.
